a885fff7-7e9c-42f8-93a1-3cd12e4474ce.summary: In Cover Fire, you have received the call of duty to be the shooter who leads a squad of veterans through besieged cities, deserts and fields taken over by guerrillas, and defeat all kinds of enemies in the war with the greatest graphic and arsenal. It's time to take action on the battlefield.
